'''Mary-Ellen Jenkins''' is the girl that [[Phoebe Buffay|Phoebe]] sets [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]] up with for the blind date. She was portrayed by [[Dedee Pfeiffer]] in "[[The One With The Pediatrician]]".

During Phoebe's wedding with [[Mike Hannigan]], she mentions Mary-Ellen in her rehearsal speech and reveals that she couldn't attend as she was in rehab.
